      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WEST ON MIRRA (1) showed good early speed and led throughout to score her maiden two back then finished eighth last start and beaten 16 lengths at this track over 488m (29.06). Returns to the course where she won her maiden. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. MATTE BLACK (2) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Cannington over 520m behind Hunter (31.08) in a Novice race. Was in the money the start prior. Must be included in calculations. SUNSET AUGUSTUS (5) stalked the pace when winning a maiden two back then finished seventh last start and beaten 14 lengths at this track over 400m (23.78). Can feature with the right run. AKERMANIS (3) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage 4 lengths away in second (27.92). Overdue and gets his chance.",
